description:
Syncfusion Dashboard Viewer Javascript is a content package having the supported scripts, themes, fonts and cultures for rendering the dashboard viewer. On embedding the dashboard viewer in any of the supported platform, the package is used to refer the static contents for the dashboard rendering in an application.

Learn more: https://www.syncfusion.com/products/dashboard/viewer?utm_source=nuget&utm_medium=listing

Documentation: https://help.syncfusion.com/dashboard-platform/dashboard-sdk/overview?utm_source=nuget&utm_medium=listing
